PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the ALEXIS INDIAN BAND surrenders, for an indefinite term, all of its rights and interests in and to the mines, minerals, oil and gas that may be found to exist within, upon or under certain reserve lands in Alberta, for the purpose of allowing the Crown to issue leases, licences and permits to third parties for the extraction and removal of the minerals and for oil and gas exploration and development.
Attachments
precis:
Acceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the ALEXIS INDIAN BAND surrenders, for
an indefinite term, all of its rights and interests in and to the mines,
minerals, oil and gas that may be found to exist within, upon or under
certain reserve lands in Alberta, for the purpose of allowing the Crown to
issue leases, licences and permits to third parties for the extraction and
removal of the minerals and for oil and gas exploration and development.
